This awesome plugin uses Web AI to read your audience's expressions in real-time in Google Meet meetings and help you to get valuable insights into audience reactions, fostering a more interactive and engaging online communication experience.

Unlike traditional methods, "Meet the Meeting" prioritizes user privacy by ensuring that 𝗻𝗼 𝗱𝗮𝘁𝗮 𝗶𝘀 𝘀𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝘁𝗼 𝗲𝘅𝘁𝗲𝗿𝗻𝗮𝗹 𝘀𝗲𝗿𝘃𝗲𝗿𝘀. The entire process occurs within the user's browser, guaranteeing a secure and private experience. Moreover, we believe in transparency and collaboration, which is why the plugin's code is open-source and accessible to all at https://github.com/hugozanini/meet-the-meeting.
